<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="29" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="29">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="29">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Yuezb., M. Bona &amp; I. Genc" authorityYear="2015" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Centaurea ziganensis" order="Asterales" pageId="2" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ziganensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="29">Centaurea ziganensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is related to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hub - Mor" authorityYear="1967" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Centaurea drabifolioides" order="Asterales" pageId="2" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="drabifolioides">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="29">Centaurea drabifolioides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, from which it differs mainly in its 2-4 (-8) branched and non-winged stem (not simple and winged), median phyllary appendages with 4-6 pairs of cilia (not 5-10); achenes 4.5-5 mm long, oblong, straw-colored, striate (not 5.5-6 mm long, lanceolate, blackish-chestnut, shiny); pappus straw-colored (not blackish-chestnut).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
